MLOPS:
=============================
MLOps refers to a practice and discipline within Machine learning that aims to unify and streamline
the machine Learning system, dev and operations
It involves collaboration between data scientists, ML engineers and IT professionals to automate and optimize 
the end to end lifecycle of ML application

based on the example we make below conclusions:
============================================
1. Data management system 
2. Version control system 
3. Automation - pipeline
4. Experiment tracking
5. Delivering
6. Monitoring/ feedback ->Retraining
7. Setup new infrastructure 
8. licenses and security

MLOPS -> DEVOPS + data engineering
We need to know how to make ML models and deploy them in our environments using Devops tools 
========================================
Generative AI
=======================================
Gen AI is a class of AI
that generates models that will create new content like text, image, video That resembles human created data 

Traditionally AI was - give an input and give an output- ai tool will find patterns on the give input and output 
and give predictions

Generative AI: where we learn form the give data and generates a new data based on it

On a gen AI model -> upload lots of images of cat  and tell this is a cat->
 will analyze all the images - generate an image/data how a cat will look it.

GEN AI -> RAG - Retrival augment based chatbots

Changing it form reactive to proactive 
Add agents to your exiting ai tool -> agentic gen AI

Agentic AI means an AI system  that can act independently to achieve the desired goal
plans -> decides ->acts -> observe -> adapt

It executes tasks, its active, works in a loop.
